begin
  intro H,
  have H1 : Round Mouse := R3 Mouse H,
  have H2 : Young Mouse := R6 Mouse H1,
  have H3 : Likes Mouse Mouse := R4 Mouse H2,
  have H4 : Likes Mouse Squirrel := R8 Mouse H3,
  exact H4 H,
end
